            . I am a constable, and received him in charge; I found the property in his hat.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM DANIEL OWEN. I had just left my wife - I heard an alarm soon after; but the prisoner had turned the corner before I saw him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It was not me.</p>
